PrecisAmendments to the LAURENTIAN PILOTAGE AUTHORITY REGULATIONS which allow pilots and holders of a Class "C" pilotage certificate to perform pilotage duties in District No. 2 (Quebec-Saguenay-Les Escoumins) on vessels having a dead weight of up to 20,000 tons, and allow candidates for certification to complete their examination in two stages.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 1994-0727 Publication Date: 1994-12-14
Attachments
precis:
Amendments to the LAURENTIAN PILOTAGE AUTHORITY REGULATIONS which allow
pilots and holders of a Class "C" pilotage certificate to perform pilotage
duties in District No. 2 (Quebec-Saguenay-Les Escoumins) on vessels having
a dead weight of up to 20,000 tons, and allow candidates for certification
to complete their examination in two stages.
